Money Stuff =0A Generally companies like to deal with all their problems at=
 once. Investors =0Atend to care more about recurring earnings than one-tim=
e events, =0A=0A=0A <https://bloom.bg/4i3tDwj> =0A =0A<https://sli.bloomber=
g.com/click=3Fs=3D825881&stpe=3Ddefault&li=3D12795370&m=3D21d6dea82d6b16615=
cf44233be620525&p=3D03042025>=0A=0A=0A=0ACiti!=0A=0AGenerally companies lik=
e to deal with all their problems at once. Investors =0Atend to care more a=
bout recurring earnings than one-time events, so if you have =0Amade some m=
